00:46:07,973 --> 00:46:09,934
[Goodblood] <i>Seize supplies.
Map victories.</i>

776
00:46:10,017 --> 00:46:12,728
<i>This will keep the spirit up,
despite the UN embargo.</i>

777
00:46:12,812 --> 00:46:15,105
[Commandant] <i>Roger. Well copied, sir.</i>

778
00:46:15,189 --> 00:46:17,525
[Goodblood] <i>Our fight is a just one.</i>

779
00:46:17,608 --> 00:46:21,278
<i>Being a freedom fighter is discipline,
obedience and loyalty.</i>

780
00:46:21,362 --> 00:46:22,363
[Commandant] <i>Roger.</i>

781
00:46:22,447 --> 00:46:25,741
<i>We remain ever loyal to Supreme HQ, sir.</i>

782
00:46:25,825 --> 00:46:28,369
<i>Standing by for future orders. Over.</i>

783
00:46:28,453 --> 00:46:32,039
[Goodblood] <i>Keep moving. Keep fighting.
