Everybody, be quiet. They are coming.

811
00:48:56,476 --> 00:48:58,644
[vehicles rumbling]

812
00:49:27,339 --> 00:49:28,591
Get ready.

813
00:49:28,674 --> 00:49:30,009
[indistinct radio chatter]

814
00:49:30,843 --> 00:49:32,386
Go, go, go.

815
00:49:36,348 --> 00:49:37,349
[vehicle halts]

816
